  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/42d1794ee711c4039095403159acfa22.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GABANG: ULTIMATE is a roguelike deck-building game where you use the items in your bag to defeat your enemies and build your own deck. You go on an adventure to defeat The Devil with the mysterious bag from a goddess that holds items indefinitely. Will you be able to reach the Cursed Land safely and defeat the Devil?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/1cd1764718a5549b521cf2815da1d1c9.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own deck, with over <strong>350+ different items</strong> and multiple classes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/b18807022482df2f6102c30edb9b6a07.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies through items of your choice that are <strong>randomly</strong> placed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/4c3c7e68e393536c6c8faf356f240103.poster.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/4c3c7e68e393536c6c8faf356f240103.webm?t=1744900682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/4c3c7e68e393536c6c8faf356f240103.mp4?t=1744900682\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Complete a lot of achievements and collect <strong>various outfits</strong>!</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/42d1794ee711c4039095403159acfa22.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=130 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >GABANG: ULTIMATE is a roguelike deck-building game where you use the items in your bag to defeat your enemies and build your own deck. You go on an adventure to defeat The Devil with the mysterious bag from a goddess that holds items indefinitely. Will you be able to reach the Cursed Land safely and defeat the Devil?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/1cd1764718a5549b521cf2815da1d1c9.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Build your own deck, with over <strong>350+ different items</strong> and multiple classes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/b18807022482df2f6102c30edb9b6a07.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=260 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Defeat enemies through items of your choice that are <strong>randomly</strong> placed!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/4c3c7e68e393536c6c8faf356f240103.poster.avif?t=1744900682\" width=618 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3297050/extras/4c3c7e68e393536c6c8faf356f240103.webm?t=1744900682\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3